00:17:06.089 --> 00:17:09.770
of salsas, chili
paste, and you just

00:17:09.770 --> 00:17:14.750
begin to see how deep the
nuances of all of the pantry

00:17:14.750 --> 00:17:16.810
staples and the spices run.

00:17:16.810 --> 00:17:19.060
GONZALO GUZMAN: Which, again,
