00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:39.800
And if you love Mexican
food, you'll love it.

00:17:39.800 --> 00:17:42.750
You'll love all these flavors,
and you'll start adding, little

00:17:42.750 --> 00:17:44.350
by little, some other chilis.

00:17:44.350 --> 00:17:46.850
And why not maybe even
doing the masa if you wanted

00:17:46.850 --> 00:17:49.260
to explore a little bit more.

00:17:49.260 --> 00:17:51.680
But it's definitely for people
that really enjoy cooking

00:17:51.680 --> 00:17:53.834
and want to take that risk.

00:17:53.834 --> 00:17:55.500
STACY ADIMONDO:
