00:18:05.784 --> 00:18:07.700
You know the difference
between a sweet potato

00:18:07.700 --> 00:18:09.991
and a white potato and what
not, and he's like, it just

00:18:09.991 --> 00:18:11.000
becomes second nature.

00:18:11.000 --> 00:18:13.090
You just see them, and
you're like, right, right.

00:18:13.090 --> 00:18:14.564
Puya, arbol, this and that.

00:18:14.564 --> 00:18:16.730
GONZALO GUZMAN: Takes time,
